import React from 'react'
import Dropdown from 'react-bootstrap/Dropdown';

function ReportCrime() {
  return (
    <form>
  <Dropdown>
      <Dropdown.Toggle variant="success" id="dropdown-basic">
      Type of Crime
      </Dropdown.Toggle>

      <Dropdown.Menu className='m'>
        <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-1">Rape / Sexual Assault </Dropdown.Item>
        <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-2">Assault</Dropdown.Item>
        <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-3">Weapons </Dropdown.Item>
        <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-4">Drugs</Dropdown.Item>
        <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-5">Alcohol </Dropdown.Item>
        <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-6">Larceny / Theft</Dropdown.Item>
        <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-7">Vandelism </Dropdown.Item>
       < Dropdown.Divider />
            <Dropdown.Item eventKey="4">other</Dropdown.Item>
   
        
      </Dropdown.Menu>
    </Dropdown>
    </form>
  )
}

export default ReportCrime
